import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import App from "./App"
import Signup from "./Signup"
import "./style.css"


ReactDOM.render(
	<Router history={browserHistory}>  
    	<Route exact path="/" component={App} />
    	<Route path="/signup" component={Signup} />
  	</Router>,
	document.getElementById("root")
)
